sentences.en: Dissatisfaction with the government has grown beyond belief.
sentences.cn: 对政府的不满已经达到令人难以置信的程度。

sentences.en: Many people have expressed their dissatisfaction with the arrangement.
sentences.cn: 许多人表示对这一安排不满。

sentences.en: She has already expressed her dissatisfaction with this aspect of the policy.
sentences.cn: 她已对政策的这方面表示了不满。
